				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: What types of armor would you choose to equip?<a name="26989"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 11 04 12:22 PM</span></td>
